{
  "stem": "1061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were caught in the cows and people and-- and-- and horses and peasants and the Jews, and everybody mixed in on the road into the forest.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And during the night-- of course, we thought, meanwhile, that Starachowice was just gonna be wiped off the earth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And meanwhile we were sitting in these forests.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the German airplanes came down with the reflectors on their airplanes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were shooting people down in the forest, because, you know, there's a clearing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people would go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the cows would-- you would hear the cows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you would hear the dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whatever it is, whether they heard it in the airplanes or not, they came and they shot us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And finally-- of course, we were not hit during that night shooting when they would sort of pick us-- pick up the groups that they wanted to shoot at.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But eventually, as we moved on, we were caught in a valley between the Polish units on one side, on a sort of-- it wasn't a hill-- in a type of hilly area-- and the German units on the other.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were caught in the middle, in the crossfire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this was just a horrendously frightening experience, because this was really my first war experience.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And mother insisted that we will wear our best clothes, the newest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had a pair of shoes, brand new shows bought for the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I put on these shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was the biggest mistake I ever made, because very soon-- it was a very hot, this September, very extremely hot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were overdressed because we wore all that stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Mother said, you know, it might be cold, whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had the worst blisters and had to take my shoes off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the PS to this whole story is that after being shot at by the German airplanes that we lowering-- lowered themselves over forest, after being caught-- caught in the crossfire, we came back and found out that nothing happened in town, absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "One bomb fell somewhere that didn't even destroy anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was sort of like a-- I don't know if it was a reawakening, but maybe this was a sign that things are not what they seem to be, or whatever it is that you are expecting might not really turn out that way, because in fact, that September 1939 is when whatever was planned-- anti-aircraft were digging ditches-- whatever was done, none of that was used.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "People were killed by whatever happened that was not expected.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went back to our home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything was left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, we ate and left everything, because you know, the evacuation was announced.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we came back, everything was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing is, of course, that we lived on the main street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is 1939, September 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were allowed to live on that street for a few more months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no special clothes in ghetto organized in Starachowice, but what they did is they cleared that street, which was called [INAUDIBLE], named after the Polish Marshal Pilsudski.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That street was cleared, and we were among the first ones to have to leave our home, and got resettled closer to the-- like there was a square.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then eventually, we found ourselves again in the wrong place, because they were clearing that street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had three more residences, three, after we left our original residence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had three more residences in the same town, but not in an enclosed ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Poles who lived where they lived were allowed to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "However, the Jews were being squeezed out of certain streets into that other district.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the last place where we lived was-- it was a Christian family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was a teamster.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Had a horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they had a little house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they gave us one big room with a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they had the other part of the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I will never forget-- the wife was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she was working the horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she was washing the horses and feeding them and all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and then I see my mother-- I know that the woman was gonna have a baby.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, I-- I knew just that much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But all of a sudden, mother shushed me and she showed-- she told us to go somewhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she was cooking boiling water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The woman was with the horses five minutes before, and she was giving birth five minutes after.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my mother was attending her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And of course, the children shouldn't know what it was or how it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
